Package com.vmware.vapi.metadata Description

The com.vmware.vapi.metadata package provides metadata interfaces. These are interfaces that provide different facets of API information. Clients can use these interfaces to:
  • Discover APIs available in the infrastructure.
  • Fetch metadata that can be used to build presentation layers like CLI, REST, etc.
  • Fetch authentication and authorization metadata.
